    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10099178>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Digital Images of claspers of Lynceus. A, L. tatei (from Serpentine, WA, WAM 51609); B, L. tatei (from Armadale WA, MZ Collection); C, L. macleayanus (from Brooms Head, NSW, AM P89072); D, L. baylyi sp.nov. (from Washington Rocks, WA, WAM 51581); E.L. magdaleanae sp.nov. (from Yanneymooning Rock, WA, WAM 51604); F, L. susanneae sp. nov. (from Cocklebiddy, WA, WAM C51326)" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10099178/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10099180>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Resting eggs of Lynceus. A. L. macleayanus; B, L. tatei; C, L. argillaphilus sp. nov.; D, L. baylyi sp. nov.; E, L. magdaleanae sp. nov.; F, L. susanneae sp. nov. Scale bars 50 ųm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10099180/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10099182>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. L. tatei, A–F male: A, carapace; B, dorsal view of head; C, lateral view of head; D, first antenna; E, second antenna; F, clasper (endites III to VI of thoracopod 1); G–J female; G dorsal view of head; H, lateral view of head; J, lamina abdominalis, anal plate and last somite. Scale bars 1 mm, except for D which it represents 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10099182/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10099184>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. SEMs of Lynceus species: A, L. baylyi sp. nov., male body in carapace; B, L. baylyi sp. nov. clasper; C, L. tatei female body in carapace; D, L. tatei female lamina abdominalis; E, L. baylyi sp. nov. female right posteriolaterial plate; F, L. baylyi sp. nov. female left posteriolateral plate. Scale A, C 1 mm, B,D,E,F 100 ųm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10099184/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

